description:
GPT-crafted control software and graphical user interface for Keithley 2400 Source Measure Units and global optimization algorithm. It contains Numba-compatible self-adaptive differential evolution algorithm for optimization tasks.

This software is comprised of two repositories: 
https://github.com/NREL/Keithley_GPT
https://github.com/NREL/DE
name: I-V characterization and parameter extraction tool [SWR-24-59]
